snippet.title: Khimera Puzzle Island Trailer
snippet.description:
STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1217830/Khimera_Puzzle_Island/

In a world where numbers dictate squares, one chimera has the audacity to stand up and fight... with her MIND!

Hide your Sunday puzzle page, Chelshia is back in her most (only) puzzling adventure yet!

Web: http://www.suitgames.com
Tweets: https://twitter.com/suitsnsandals
Discord: https://discord.gg/xAz94jK
